Once up on a time , in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon{berry} tree,
which was on the bankes of the river. In the same Forest,there lived a Crocodile and his wife .....

One day, the Crocodile came to the bankes of the river and rested under the tree. 
THe kind hearted monkey offered some fruits. the Crocodile cmae back the next day for more fruit. as he love them.
as day pased the Crocodile and the monkey became good friend.

One day, the monkey send some fruit for the Crocodile wife. 
She eat the fruit and like them but was jeslous as she did not like her husband spending time with the monkey.
she toled her husband,"if the fruit are so juicy , i wondey how sweet the monkey's heart would be".
get me the heart of the monkey. the Crocodile was not willing to kill his friend but had no choice.
